name: INSaveProfileInCarIntentHandling
desc: The handler interface for saving vehicle environment settings to a user-specified profile.DeprecatedThis intent is no longer available. You may define a custom intent instead. For more information, see Deprecated SiriKit Intent Domains.

items.name: func resolveProfileNumber(for: INSaveProfileInCarIntent, with: (INIntegerResolutionResult) -> Void)
items.desc: Resolves the profile index in which to save any settings.

items.name: func resolveProfileName(for: INSaveProfileInCarIntent, with: (INStringResolutionResult) -> Void)
items.desc: Resolves the profile name in which to save any settings.

items.name: func confirm(intent: INSaveProfileInCarIntent, completion: (INSaveProfileInCarIntentResponse) -> Void)
items.desc: Confirms whether you can save the settings to the designated profile.

items.name: func handle(intent: INSaveProfileInCarIntent, completion: (INSaveProfileInCarIntentResponse) -> Void)
items.desc: Handles saving any settings to the designated profile.
